comments: Reaves (LAL) brings his hands toward the ball and marginal brush contact occurs with Doncic's (DAL) arm after he secures the rebound.
Lively II (DAL) firms up in Davis' (LAL) path and marginal contact occurs as they disengage during the screen.
Davis (LAL) makes direct contact with the ball, blocking Williams' (DAL) jump shot attempt, prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Hardaway Jr. (DAL) does not beat Reaves (LAL) to the spot prior to body contact occurring that affects Reaves' SQBR.
Exum (DAL) aligns along Reaves' (LAL) path and absorbs the marginal contact at the start of Reaves' drive.
Hachimura (LAL) rests his hand on Doncic's (DAL) side and the marginal contact dissolves shortly thereafter.
Doncic (DAL) and James (LAL) come together at the same spot on the floor and the contact is marginal.
James (LAL) comes to, rather than through, Doncic's (DAL) space and the contact during James' dribble is marginal.
Doncic (DAL) brings his hand toward the ball and marginal brush contact occurs with James' (LAL) arm during his dribble drive.
Lively II (DAL) contests the layup attempt and marginal contact occurs with James' (LAL) arm after the release.
Doncic (DAL) is assessed an unsportsmanlike technical foul.
The loose ball goes off of Doncic's (DAL) extended leg and then off of Lively II's (DAL) foot planted on the ground, but neither player intentionally kicks the ball.
James (LAL) and Williams (DAL) engage as the screen is set and the contact is marginal.
Davis (LAL) turns his body as he braces for the contact with Williams (DAL) during the pick and the contact is marginal.
Doncic (DAL) brings his weight up as he establishes himself in Reaves' (LAL) path and Doncic absorbs the marginal contact during the driving shot attempt.
Lively II (DAL) cleanly blocks the shot attempt prior to when the ball reaches its apex.
Reaves (LAL) moves to, rather than through, Doncic's (DAL) space as the two players come together during the driving shot attempt and the contact is marginal.
Prince (LAL) brings his hand around toward the ball and marginal brush contact occurs with Doncic's (DAL) arm during the drive.
Davis (LAL) momentarily clasps and releases Lively II's (DAL) arm during the rebounding opportunity and the contact is marginal.
After communicating with the Replay Center, it is determined that James (LAL) releases his shot attempt before the expiration of the game clock and the basket counts.
